                  </hi>. I am in the service of Mr. Burgess, in Long Acre, a pawnbroker—I produce this flannel petticoat, which was pawned by the prisoner on the afternoon of the 7th of Nov., for 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.—I live about a quarter of a mile from the prosecutor.</p>
